### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{code}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "name": "Smoke Test",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "program": "SISTEMAS"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Get signed photo URL (use token from Login response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me/photo-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Put photo (1x1 png)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/photo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "photo": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR4nGNgYAAAAAMAASsJTYQAAAAASUVORK5CYII="
}

### Get signed photo URL again
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me/photo-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete photo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/me/photo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

